  "grammarSections": [
    {
      "type": "explanation",
      "title": { "en": "Regular Affirmative Tú Commands", "nl": "Regelmatige Bevestigende Tú Bevelen" },
      "content": {
        "en": "A regular affirmative command is formed by simply dropping the **s** from the second-person singular conjugated form:\n\n**Hablas** → **¡Habla!** (Speak!)\n**Comes** → **¡Come!** (Eat!)\n**Vives** → **¡Vive!** (Live!)",
        "nl": "Een regelmatig bevestigend bevel wordt gevormd door de **s** weg te laten van de tweede persoon enkelvoud:\n\n**Hablas** → **¡Habla!** (Spreek!)\n**Comes** → **¡Come!** (Eet!)\n**Vives** → **¡Vive!** (Leef!)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "explanation",
      "title": { "en": "Regular Negative Tú Commands", "nl": "Regelmatige Ontkennende Tú Bevelen" },
      "content": {
        "en": "A regular negative command is formed as follows:\n1. Begin with the present tense first-person singular (**yo**) form.\n2. Remove the **-o** ending (the \"yo stem\").\n3. For **-ar** verbs, add **-es**. For **-er** and **-ir** verbs, add **-as**.\n\n**hablo** → **habl-** → **¡No hables!**\n**como** → **com-** → **¡No comas!**\n**escribo** → **escrib-** → **¡No escribas!**",
        "nl": "Een ontkennend bevel wordt als volgt gevormd:\n1. Begin met de eerste persoon enkelvoud (**yo**) vorm.\n2. Verwijder de **-o** uitgang.\n3. Voeg **-es** toe voor **-ar** werkwoorden, **-as** voor **-er** en **-ir** werkwoorden.\n\n**hablo** → **habl-** → **¡No hables!**\n**como** → **com-** → **¡No comas!**\n**escribo** → **escrib-** → **¡No escribas!**"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "rule_box",
      "title": { "en": "Spelling Changes", "nl": "Spellingveranderingen" },
      "content": {
        "en": "Before the letter **e**, the following orthographic changes apply:\n• **c → qu** (No toques el piano!)\n• **g → gu** (No juegues al béisbol!)\n• **z → c** (No comiences!)",
        "nl": "Vóór de letter **e** gelden de volgende spellingveranderingen:\n• **c → qu** (No toques el piano!)\n• **g → gu** (No juegues al béisbol!)\n• **z → c** (No comiences!)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "explanation",
      "title": { "en": "Irregular Tú Commands", "nl": "Onregelmatige Tú Bevelen" },
      "content": {
        "en": "There are very few verbs with irregular tú commands. Listed below are the most common:\n\n| Infinitive | Affirmative | Negative |\n|---|---|---|\n| decir | **di** | no digas |\n| hacer | **haz** | no hagas |\n| ir | **ve** | no vayas |\n| poner | **pon** | no pongas |\n| salir | **sal** | no salgas |\n| ser | **sé** | no seas |\n| tener | **ten** | no tengas |\n| venir | **ven** | no vengas |",
        "nl": "Er zijn slechts weinig werkwoorden met onregelmatige tú bevelen:\n\n| Infinitief | Bevestigend | Ontkennend |\n|---|---|---|\n| decir | **di** | no digas |\n| hacer | **haz** | no hagas |\n| ir | **ve** | no vayas |\n| poner | **pon** | no pongas |\n| salir | **sal** | no salgas |\n| ser | **sé** | no seas |\n| tener | **ten** | no tengas |\n| venir | **ven** | no vengas |"
      }
    }
  ],
